Description

Our 5 piece basic hygiene kit provides the essentials packed into a travel-sized re-closable bag. This kit is an ideal way to provide personal care items that allow any individual to start or end their day. Customers love to use these care packages at donation, giveaway nonprofit events, disaster relief, Airbnb and even just the guest room!

Each kit includes: 1 oz. Biovida Shampoo,  1/2 Oz Deodorant Soap , Toothpaste,  Toothbrush, Black Comb all in a reusable zip lock bag.

• 5 ITEMS PER KIT

• 96 KITS PER CASE

• PREPACKAGED KITS IN RECLOSABLE BAGS

• READY FOR DISTRIBUTION

• GREAT FOR ANY OCCASION

• Item Dimensions: 10X14X9

BackpacksUSA.com Return Policy

Thank you for shopping with BackpacksUSA. We want you to be completely confident in your purchase. Please note you have up to 14 days to inspect and return any defective items and/or any missing items. After 14 days no refunds/credits can processed. Please return defective or incorrect products in original shipping carton, with all original packaging in tact. Once items have been inspected, the refund/credit will be issued. In some cases photographic evidence of damage/defect may be required. Please note the customer is responsible for paying return shipping cost, as free shipping is provided for initial shipment by BackpacksUSA. Clearance items can only be returned for an in-house credit, and only if said items are defective. For any return shipping questions, please contact us at 305-400-9040.
